<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Payment Success & Tickets</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>Thank you for your purchase! Your payment for the order <strong>{{orderId}}</strong> has been successfully processed.</p>
    <p>Here are the download links for your tickets to <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>:</p>
    <ul>
        {{#each ticketUrls}}
        <li><a href="{{this}}">Download Ticket</a></li>
        {{/each}}
    </ul>
    <p>Please present the QR Code on your ticket(s) at the venue entrance.</p>
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p><strong>Ticketing Team</strong></p>
</body>
</html>
